{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b4f8c3d2-0a5e-4b2f-d3e4-f5a6b7890123",
    "name": "Mobile API — Full roundtrip (OTP → cart → booking)",
    "description": "End-to-end **/mobile** flow for python-graphql-api.\n\n**Run Collection Runner in order** (top to bottom).\n\n**Variables** (collection → Variables):\n- `baseUrl` — e.g. `http://localhost:5002`\n- `mobilePhone` — 10-digit Indian mobile (e.g. `9876543210`)\n- `otp` — optional; auto-filled from `debugOtp` when `MOBILE_OTP_DEBUG=true` on request-otp\n\n**Auto-set by tests:** `otp`, `mobileAccessToken`, `userId`, `addressId`, `addressId2`, `categoryId`, `serviceId1`, `serviceId2`, `bookingId`\n\n**Notes:**\n- **Verify OTP** sends `firstName` / `lastName` (profile bootstrap).\n- **Subcategories** need a **numeric** `categoryId` (from `categories` table). If `/mobile/home` uses legacy string category ids, step 8 may return **400** — set `categoryId` manually in variables or ignore that step.\n- **Cart** needs at least one active service in DB; placeholder media URLs must be **HTTPS** if your app validates.\n- **cart_items** table must exist (`scripts/create_cart_items_table.sql` + alter if needed).\n- Clear cart before re-running booking steps or use a fresh user.\n\n\n**Status codes:** See `docs/API_STATUS_CODES.md` and GET probe output `docs/api_sanity_report.md`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
